those assassins
would've gotten rid of me

22
00:02:53,659 --> 00:02:56,040
had Marquis Pei not saved me.

23
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:58,140
Marquis Pei,

24
00:02:59,300 --> 00:03:00,100
let me offer you a toast.

25
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:03,040
It's all thanks to His Majesty's grace.

26
00:03:03,380 --> 00:03:04,360
I barely

27
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:05,820
did the minimum.

28
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:07,800
Today,

29
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:10,100
it was fortunate

30
00:03:10,100 --> 00:03:11,420
that the envoys of Wei State were saved.

31
00:03:12,380 --> 00:03:14,239
Once the peace treaty
is officially signed,

32
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:16,540
I will hold a grand celebration

33
00:03:16,540 --> 00:03:19,100
on Qinghui River.

34
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:21,480
Your Majesty is wise.

35
00:03:21,820 --> 00:03:23,480
Your Majesty is wise.

36
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:24,420
Your Majesty is wise.

37
00:03:25,380 --> 00:03:26,200
Pei Yan,

38
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:29,239
you should be in charge
of the signing ceremony.

39
00:03:29,580 --> 00:03:30,200
Yes, Your Majesty.

40
00:03:36,140 --> 00:03:37,200
Sanlang.

41
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:40,040
How are your ears doing?

42
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:41,760
Your Majesty,

43
00:03:41,980 --> 00:03:43,439
please stop teasing me.

44
00:03:43,920 --> 00:03:45,320
That old woman almost

45
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,600
bit half of my ear off.

46
00:03:47,100 --> 00:03:48,480
It was so embarrassing.

47
00:03:53,820 --> 00:03:55,040
I was negligent.

48
00:03:55,700 --> 00:03:57,480
That's why Sanlang was wounded
by that crook.

49
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:59,140
I'll drink three cups as punishment.

50
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:00,540
Lord Pei.

51
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,700
You shouldn't blame me for being angry

52
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:05,700
and punish them by the law
without permission.

53
00:04:06,540 --> 00:04:08,380
You got caught off guard
and failed, huh?

54
00:04:11,140 --> 00:04:12,100
Don't be upset.

55
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:13,920
Drink up.

56
00:04:14,700 --> 00:04:16,940
Today's a joyous occasion.

57
00:04:18,799 --> 00:04:20,140
Your Majesty, you're right.

58
00:04:20,919 --> 00:04:22,039
At this moment,

59
00:04:22,359 --> 00:04:23,820
we should drink

60
00:04:24,099 --> 00:04:24,799
and enjoy sword dances.

61
00:04:25,859 --> 00:04:27,659
Since today's a joyous occasion,

62
00:04:28,099 --> 00:04:29,159
allow me

63
00:04:29,919 --> 00:04:30,719
to perform a dance.

64
00:05:16,620 --> 00:05:20,739
♪The wind sighs as catkins fill the city♪

65
