♪The cuckoo cries as it longs for home♪

66
00:05:25,900 --> 00:05:29,759
♪Home is nowhere in sight on the difficult path♪

67
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:34,339
♪As melancholic as the layers of sand♪

68
